author: Zeta Ret
text: self rendering html element outside canvas represented as normal stage child in the display list

public_methods.render: stage*: zetaret.global.packages.clockwork.controllers.Stage2DController, renderer*: zetaret.global.packages.clockwork.context.ContextRenderer, ctx*: CanvasRenderingContext2D, t*: Array, ct*: Array; return zetaret.global.packages.clockwork.ui::HTMLElement

descriptions.ctxreset: auto reset native context transform, alpha and color transform during self rendering
descriptions.pointer: allow native dom pointer over html element or traverse through canvas display list interaction controller
descriptions.zindex: auto compute html element css z-index based on canvas stage index of child, disable to use custom z-index i.e. negative values under the canvas element

HTMLElement.this: canrender is auto set to true and uses overriden render method
